made me feel better.

00:15.900 --> 00:18.460
Can you imagine Shirley
in her little cheer—

00:18.500 --> 00:19.700
Oh, my god.

00:19.700 --> 00:21.460
Denny, I got in!
I'm in the coast guard!

00:21.500 --> 00:22.300
What?

00:22.300 --> 00:23.060
–Uh…
–Am I in?

00:23.100 --> 00:25.360
I don't know,
did you get a letter?

00:25.400 --> 00:27.800
–I'm in!
–Ah! Ha ha!

00:27.800 --> 00:31.298
–We're in the coast guard!
–We're in the coast guard!

