01:45.300 --> 01:46.760
I'm gonna let it go
this one time,

01:46.800 --> 01:47.860
but I'm going to have to

01:47.900 --> 01:50.860
make a thorough inspection
of your flotation devices.

01:50.900 --> 01:52.200
Brand-new.

01:52.400 --> 01:53.400
Well-done.

01:53.400 --> 01:55.500
Okay, Denny,
the situation is—

01:58.400 --> 02:02.000
How did you possibly
get out of your clothes so fast?

02:02.000 --> 02:03.716
Semper paratus, my friend.

